Package edu.handong.csee.java.lab07.prob2

Class Chicken

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.handong.csee.java.lab07.prob2.Chicken

  • public class Chicken
extends java.lang.Object
    Chicken class creates various chicken menus with price and rating and shows each menu information.

    This class uses various setter and getter methods to set various values of chicken menu. This class also has two constructors: one empty and one with 3 parameters passed.

    Author:
    Jun Seob Lee
